{"tid":1670570,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共一招加泰就打到香港人進退兩難！？再唔做野就比支共食住上","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:40:28.000Z","uid":175453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b9d4bcf41c8ad0d613f4fd99d25487052f0013","tid":1670570,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"依家連登對加泰睇法兩極化<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去</span></span><br />\n支持加獨<br />\n同美國反面<br />\n但即使去 人數一定唔多 成個觀感仲差過唔去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">結果</span></span><br />\n香港人普遍唔支持加泰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔去</span></span><br />\n口講對抗極權最前線<br />\n但眼前只有自己利益<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">結果</span></span><br />\n外國對香港人評價一落千丈<br />\n<br />\n咁我地應該點做？<br />\n去唔去都有機會對香港造成負面影響<br />\n咁我地唯有<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">改</span></span><br />\n將加泰集會改為支援世界民主自由抗爭作主題<br />\n一來可以照幫加泰打氣<br />\n二來為我地集會正名<br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8872b4e83178456a45e84b89339b71f53662f1d","tid":1670570,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"093f82651a75d1d277bc80f14ef2e1a0ef125719","tid":1670570,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"[可唔可以大和解］加泰搞手 全香港人求下你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669934</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef9a3c1f944fbdb609d5ffde4389eeeee08e4b82","tid":1670570,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"［反加泰行動］星期四搵其他地方搞全球反警暴集會！並強調參加撐加泰集會嘅都係五毛扮反送中人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670501\" 